HR Analytics Dashboar – Power BI

Why HR Analytics Matters? 
HR Analytics helps organizations make **data-driven decisions** to enhance workforce management, improve employee engagement, and reduce attrition. By leveraging insights from HR data, businesses can optimize hiring, track performance trends, and foster a more productive work environment.  

 **Key Benefits:**  
**Employee Retention** – Identify factors affecting attrition and take proactive measures.  
**Workforce Diversity & Inclusion** – Track diversity metrics to build a balanced workplace.  
**Performance & Productivity** – Measure employee efficiency and engagement.  
**Compensation & Benefits Analysis** – Ensure competitive salaries and incentives.  

This **Power BI dashboard** provides **real-time HR insights**, enabling organizations to make informed workforce decisions.
